{"tid":1957688,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黨鐵宣布縮班次","createTime":"2020-04-04T05:51:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T06:53:06.000Z","uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"71a14f2fe30b9e23ec49e3ce6afc400df23ab6ed","tid":1957688,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:51:55.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】港鐵下周五起縮4路綫班次服務 迪士尼綫暫停<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/e-qxVP6gagQc3279xQtZwL-bDpM=/414x232/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/XP43W4W6ERMFFBKABEG3OAZ7NY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2Fe-qxVP6gagQc3279xQtZwL-bDpM%3D%2F414x232%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FXP43W4W6ERMFFBKABEG3OAZ7NY.jpg&h=0926915a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵宣佈由下周五（10日）起調整4條路綫的服務，包括機場快綫、東涌綫、屯馬綫一期及迪士尼綫的服務。另外，同日起會暫停香港站及九龍站的市區預辦登機服務。<br />\n<br />\n同時，港鐵將於同日（10日）起暫停香港站及九龍站的市區預辦登機服務，由香港站或九龍站往返各主要酒店及鐵路轉綫站的機場快綫免費穿梭巴士服務亦會暫停。<br />\n<br />\n機場快綫列車在平日繁忙時間的班次將會維持每15分鐘一班車，非繁忙時間則調整至每30分鐘一班車。<br />\n<br />\n東涌綫及屯馬綫一期在平日非繁忙時段、周末及公眾假期將維持平均約10分鐘一班。乘客的候車時間平均會延長多一至兩分鐘。至於迪士尼綫亦將由同日起暫停服務，港鐵公司將安排接駁巴士來往欣澳站及迪士尼站。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200404/3GY3UVR3J2MFWN3JHIBV5ACNPU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200404%2F3GY3UVR3J2MFWN3JHIBV5ACNPU%2F&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQygV2WuQOZSh7uXaWrws9Zz8%3D&h=155bcbde\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200404%2F3GY3UVR3J2MFWN3JHIBV5ACNPU%2F&h=8fe19359\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/20200404/3GY3UVR3J2MFWN3JHIBV5ACNPU/</a>"},{"pid":"73dd33892ed2a50cf1f0946e155557060e99ea26","tid":1957688,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:53:47.000Z","msg":"不如停駛"},{"pid":"d427db3ae5cc35204